OL,3,CCodeine cough syrup to be banned from
OL,4,Cpharmacies over opioid abuse fears
OL,6,FCough syrup containing codeine is set
OL,7,Fto be banned from pharmacies over
OL,8,Ffears of opioid addiction as people
OL,9,Fmix it with lemonade, officials have
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FThe cough syrup codeine linctus will
OL,13,Fnow only be available to patients with
OL,14,Fa prescription due to concerns
OL,15,Fsurrounding abuse and addiction.
OL,17,FThe medicine, which was previously
OL,18,Favailable to buy in pharmacies, has
OL,19,Fbeen reclassified by the Medicines and
OL,20,FHealthcare products Regulatory Agency
OL,21,F(MHRA).
