OL,3,CCodeine cough syrup to be banned from
OL,4,Cpharmacies over opioid abuse fears
OL,6,FIt is recommended to ease the symptoms
OL,7,Fof a dry cough in adults and children
OL,8,Fover the age of 12 with no breathing
OL,9,Fdifficulties, but experts have found
OL,10,Fan uptick in reports that the opioid
OL,11,Fis being used as a recreational drug.
OL,13,FThe decision to make it prescription-
OL,14,Fonly was made following an MHRA
OL,15,Fconsultation with experts and
OL,16,Fhealthcare professionals.
OL,18,FThe MHRA also heard that pressure was
OL,19,Fbeing put on pharmacists to sell
OL,20,Fcodeine linctus to addicts.
