OL,3,CCodeine cough syrup to be banned from
OL,4,Cpharmacies over opioid abuse fears
OL,6,FDr Alison Cave, chief safety officer
OL,7,Fat MHRA, said: "Patient safety is our
OL,8,Ftop priority.
OL,10,F"Codeine linctus is an effective
OL,11,Fmedicine for long term dry cough, but
OL,12,Fas it is an opioid, its misuse and
OL,13,Fabuse can have major health
OL,14,Fconsequences."
OL,16,FFigures released by the Office for
OL,17,FNational Statistics (ONS), and cited
OL,18,Fby the MHRA, revealed deaths involving
OL,19,Fcodeine more than doubled in a decade,
OL,20,Fjumping from 88 in 2011 to 200 in 2021.
