OL,3,CCodeine cough syrup to be banned from
OL,4,Cpharmacies over opioid abuse fears
OL,6,FThe MHRA has also received three case
OL,7,Freports describing addiction
OL,8,Fspecifically with codeine linctus.
OL,10,FDr Cave added: "Codeine addiction can
OL,11,Fbe a gradual process. If you have been
OL,12,Ftaking it for a long time and want to
OL,13,Fstop, you can talk to your healthcare
OL,14,Fprovider and reduce the amount you
OL,15,Ftake slowly.
