OL,6,F"If you feel that you are addicted or
OL,7,Fhave concerns for someone who has been
OL,8,Fusing codeine linctus for too long,
OL,9,Fyou can seek advice on the NHS
OL,10,Fwebsite. Support groups and self-help
OL,11,Fgroups are also available such as Talk
OL,12,Fto FRANK."
OL,14,FThe Royal Pharmaceutical Society (RPS)
OL,15,Fhas welcomed the decision to
OL,16,Freclassify the medicine.
