OL,3,CCodeine cough syrup to be banned from
OL,4,Cpharmacies over opioid abuse fears
OL,6,FPresident Professor Claire Anderson
OL,7,Fsaid: "This decision not only
OL,8,Faddresses concerns about the misuse
OL,9,Fand addictive potential of codeine
OL,10,Flinctus but also underscores the
OL,11,Fimportance of prioritising patient
OL,12,Fwell-being.
OL,14,F"Many community pharmacists already no
OL,15,Flonger stock codeine linctus due to
OL,16,Fconcerns about addiction and abuse.
