OL,3,CCodeine cough syrup to be banned from
OL,4,Cpharmacies over opioid abuse fears
OL,6,F"Those that do provide it often
OL,7,Fexperience aggression from patients if
OL,8,Fthey refuse a sale because in their
OL,9,Fclinical judgement it's not
OL,10,Fappropriate to supply the medicine."
OL,12,FProf Anderson said there are "many
OL,13,Falternative non-codeine-based products
OL,14,Favailable to treat a dry cough".
OL,16,F"As the most accessible of healthcare
OL,17,Fprofessionals, community pharmacists
OL,18,Fand their teams will continue to
OL,19,Fprovide expert advice on managing dry
OL,20,Fcough and guide people towards
OL,21,Fsuitable treatments."
